21:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container-x","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"relative aspect-[16/8] overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-ink-700 shadow-lift","children":["$","$L7",null,{"src":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1800&q=80","alt":"Analytics dashboard showing organic traffic growth curve","fill":true,"priority":true,"sizes":"(min-width: 1024px) 80vw, 100vw","className":"object-cover"}]}]}]}]
22:["$","section",null,{"className":"bg-white pt-16 pb-24","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"container-x grid gap-12 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_260px]","children":[["$","article",null,{"data-progress-target":true,"className":"max-w-3xl prose-base","children":[[["$","p","0",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"Every UK SaaS founder we've spoken to in the last 18 months has been pitched the same thing: a £4–8K/month link-building retainer promising 10 'high authority' backlinks. The economics don't work. The links are increasingly cheap PBN placements that Google's link spam update neutralises within a quarter, and you're one manual action away from disaster. Here's what we do instead."}],["$","h2","1",{"id":"topical-authority","className":"font-display font-semibold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink-50 mt-14 scroll-mt-24 group","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"#topical-authority","className":"no-underline","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"Build topical authority before you build links"}],["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"ml-2 text-ember-500/0 group-hover:text-ember-500/80 transition-colors text-base","children":"#"}]]}]}],["$","p","2",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"Google's site-quality classifier rewards depth in a topic far more than it rewards a handful of high-DR backlinks. We've seen DR 22 sites outrank DR 65 sites because the smaller site had 60 interconnected articles on one tight topic — a 'topical mesh' — while the bigger site had 12 articles across 12 unrelated topics."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"The practical play: pick three pillar topics that map exactly to your product. Plan 15–20 articles per pillar across the awareness/consideration/decision stages. Ship them in 90-day sprints, not over two years. Interlink aggressively — every article should link to three siblings and one pillar."}],["$","h2","4",{"id":"programmatic","className":"font-display font-semibold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink-50 mt-14 scroll-mt-24 group","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"#programmatic","className":"no-underline","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"Programmatic SEO for long-tail queries"}],["$","span",null,{"aria-hidden":true,"className":"ml-2 text-ember-500/0 group-hover:text-ember-500/80 transition-colors text-base","children":"#"}]]}]}],["$","p","5",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"If your product has a directory dimension (integrations, templates, use cases, industries served), build a programmatic SEO layer. We've shipped programmatic pages that rank for 'X for Y' queries with zero backlinks — because the pages match search intent so cleanly that Google ranks them on relevance alone."}],["$","aside","6",{"className":"mt-8 glass-strong p-6 border-l-4 border-l-ember-500","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-ember-600","children":"Example"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-2 text-ink-100","children":"A UK fintech client built 240 programmatic pages of the form '[Accounting Software] integration with [UK Bank]'. Each page had 350 words of unique, useful content (the integration's actual capabilities). Six months later: 47K organic sessions/month from those pages alone. Backlinks acquired: 0."}]]}],["$","h2","7",{"id":"internal-linking","className":"font-display font-semibold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-ink-50 mt-14 scroll-mt-24 group","children":["$","a",null,{"href":"#internal-linking","className":"no-underline","children":[["$","span",null,{"children":"Internal linking is your biggest underused lever"}],"$L25"]}]}],"$L26","$L27","$L28","$L29","$L2a","$L2b","$L2c","$L2d"],"$L2e","$L2f","$L30","$L31"]}],"$L32"]}]}]
