29:["$","p","11",{"className":"text-ink-200 text-lg leading-relaxed mt-6","children":"Structured data won't directly improve rank but it does increase the surface area you take in the SERP — and SERP real estate is everything. FAQPage schema on articles. HowTo schema where the content actually is step-by-step. Product schema with aggregateRating on comparison pages. Review schema on case studies. Course schema if you have a learning hub."}]
